## Phase 3: User Auth (Signup / Login)
- [x] Signup endpoint — hash password, store user
- [x] Login endpoint — verify password, return JWT
- [x] WebSocket auth — validate JWT on connection
- [x] Client: Auth UI (signup/login forms, token storage)

## Phase 4: Room System
- [x] Prisma: Room model + RoomMember join table
- [x] REST: Create room, join room by ID, list user's rooms
- [x] WebSocket: Room-scoped messaging via Redis channels
- [x] Client: Room list sidebar, create/join room UI, room-scoped chat

## Phase 5: One-to-One Chat
- [x] REST: Create or get DM conversation
- [x] WebSocket: DM messaging (private channel)
- [x] Client: DM thread from user list

## Phase 6: Chat History
- [x] Save all messages (room + DM) to PostgreSQL
- [x] REST: Fetch paginated history for a room/DM
- [x] Client: Load history on room/DM open

## Phase 7: Contact List / Friends
- [x] Prisma: Friendship model (PENDING/ACCEPTED)
- [x] REST: Send request, accept/reject, list friends
- [x] Client: Friends tab, add friend, request UI

## Phase 8: Call Logs
- [x] Prisma: CallLog model
- [x] Server: Log call start/end with duration
